  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200&deg;C/ 180&deg;C (fan)/ 400&deg;F/ Gas 6</p>\r\n<p>Boil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Chop the <strong>chorizo</strong> as small as you can</p>\r\n<p>Deseed the <strong>peppers</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into bite-size pieces</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>black rice</strong> to a pot of plenty of <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Cook for 30 min or until tender&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Once cooked, drain and return to the pot</p>\r\n<p>Tip: black rice has got a bite to it, so don't worry if you think it's not cooked after 30 min, it will be!</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>saffron</strong> to a bowl and cover in 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong> and set aside</p>\r\n<p>Tip: soaking saffron in hot water infuses the water, bringing out its colour and flavour</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Carefully loosen the<strong> chicken skin</strong> from the <strong>thigh meat&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Divide the chopped&nbsp;<strong>chorizo</strong> between the <strong>chicken thighs</strong> and sandwich it between the loosened<strong> chicken skins</strong> and <strong>thigh meat</strong></p>\r\n<p>Season the stuffed<strong> chicken</strong> with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper&nbsp;</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>romano&nbsp;</strong><strong>pepper</strong>&nbsp;to a baking tray, drizzle with <strong>olive oil</strong> and sit the stuffed<strong> chicken </strong>over the peppers&nbsp;(this will prevent the peppers from burning)</p>\r\n<p>Put the tray in the oven for 25 min or until the pepper has softened and the chicken is cooked through</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>\r\n<p>Peel and chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>mayonnaise</strong> to the bowl with the <strong>saffron </strong>and water&nbsp;and mix well</p>\r\n<p>Add the&nbsp;<strong>garlic</strong> and season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> - this is your <strong>saffron aioli</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-6-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked, transfer the stuffed <strong>chicken</strong> to a clean chopping board and leave it to rest for 3-4 min</p>\r\n<p>Stir the cooked <strong>peppers</strong> and the roasting juices through the<strong> black rice</strong></p>\r\n<p>Add the chopped&nbsp;<strong>parsley</strong> and&nbsp;1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span><strong> lemon juice</strong>&nbsp;to the<strong> rice</strong> and season with both&nbsp;<strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Once rested, carefully slice the<strong> chicken</strong> with a sharp knife&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/844.step-7-x400.jpg",
